<%= h1_component text: "Mobile Inputs" %>
<%= text_component text: "Mobile input fields allow users to enter their mobile numbers." %>
<%= text_component text: "When country_code is passed as paramter, it is rendered as read only text field, else available country codes can be selected via a select control" %>

